        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>Java</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\r\n  <p>Implement authentication on the server-side.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>Server-side authentication should be used, because client-side authentication is easy to bypass.</p>\r\n  <h1>How</h1>\r\n  <p>To implement server-side authentication, use authentication controls provided by the framework, or use a well-known third-party authentication library. If you have to implement your own authentication controls, design them to perform authentication on the server-side.</p>"
